Anambra Westi bụ ọchịchị ime obodo dị n'ebe ugwu ọdịda anyanwụ nke Anambra Steeti, Naijiria

Obodo mejuputara ya bu Mmiata Anam, Odekpe,Umuoba-Abegbu Anam, Umuenwelum Anam, Owelle, Oroma-Etiti, Umueze Anam, Umudora Anam, Umuikwu Anam, Onono Anam, Ukwalla, Inoma-Akator, Nzam, Igbedor, Igbokenyi na Iyiora Anam
Isi ụlọ ọrụ na oche gọọmentị bụ Nzam
Ndi Anambra Westi so na otu ndi Igbo a na-akpo Omambala.

Anambra West nwere nnukwu mmanụ na gas, a na-egosikwa na ọ nwere mmanụ kachasị elu na Naijiria nwere nnukwu gas na mmanụ a na-emebeghị eme na Mmiata Anam, Owelle, Umuikwu, Umudora, Nzam, Odekpe na Igbedor.
